Title: Santa?
Description: Santa looks kind of sad and not at all up to the task of traveling around the world.

Title: Santa Claus Singing Jingle Bells
Description: From "Santa Claus Sings Christmas" the delightfully original Christmas CD in which Santa Claus and young friend sing your family's favorite Christmas songs. Though these songs are traditional and often heard during the holidays, they take on an original and story like quality when sung in character by these two highly talented vocal artists.

Title: The Year Without Santa Claus
Description: The Year Without a Santa Claus is a story told by Mrs. Claus, of the year that there almost wasn't a Christmas. Santa had fallen ill, and under the recommendation of his doctor, decided to issue a press release that Christmas was canceled so that he may take a holiday.
